title: Students Injured After Bus Involved In Head-On Crash
text:
Students Injured After Bus Involved In Head-On Crash February 9, 2017 12:51 PM Filed Under: School bus accident , school bus crash 
BALTIMORE (WJZ) â€” Students were injured after a school bus was involved in a head-on collision Thursday morning in Baltimore County. 
Authorities say the bus hit another vehicle head on in the 3800 block of Offutt Rd. in Randallstown. 
Two students on the bus, along with the two drivers, were reportedly taken to an area hospital with non-life threatening injuries.
